<!--X-Subject-Header-Begin-->
<h1>Developing software for IETF/IRTF groups</h1>
<hr>
<!--X-Subject-Header-End-->
<!--X-Head-of-Message-->
<ul>
<li><em>To</em>: <a href="mailto:ietf-quality%40bogus.com">ietf-quality@bogus.com</a></li>
<li><em>Subject</em>: Developing software for IETF/IRTF groups</li>
