<li><em>Date</em>: Tue, 16 Sep 2003 09:09:36 -0400</li>
<li><em>User-agent</em>: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; en-US; rv:1.4) Gecko/20030624</li>
